OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 31 May to Tue 9 JunFA
OL,6,Fmore changeable period than we have
OL,7,Fseen of late, as Atlantic weather
OL,8,Fsystems move in from the west to bring
OL,9,Fa mixture of drier spells and some
OL,10,Fshowers, or longer spells of rain at
OL,11,Ftimes. The rain will likely be
OL,12,Fheaviest in parts of the west and
OL,13,Fnorthwest, with the best of the drier
OL,14,Fconditions more likely towards the
OL,15,Fsouth and east. Temperatures will be
OL,16,Fnear-normal overall, with the warmest
OL,17,Fspots most likely across eastern
OL,18,Fareas. It will also be breezy at
OL,19,Ftimes, most especially across
OL,20,Fnorthwestern areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
